this package provide a glob pattern matching behaviour.

package org.vostok.glob provide 2 classes :

  • Glob : a glob matcher, same signature as regular Matcher.
  • PriorityGlogList : specialised PriorityList to work with glob object.

package org.vostok.io.filter :

  • some filter for common file extension (jar, xml,etc.. ) using glob.

Depend on : VostokIOLib
